<h2>
    Why Medford is a Hidden Gem for Salmon Anglers
</h2>
<p>
    Tucked in the heart of the Rogue Valley, <strong>Medford, Oregon</strong> sits in prime proximity to some of the best salmon fishing rivers in the Pacific Northwest. While Portland and the Columbia often take center stage, Medford offers a quieter, more accessible salmon experience that’s just as rewarding—without the crowds.
</p>
<h3>
    Geographical Advantage
</h3>
<p>
    Medford lies near several productive rivers including the Rogue, Applegate, and Illinois. These waters are known for healthy salmon populations, scenic landscapes, and a variety of fishing options suitable for all skill levels.
</p>
<h3>
    Access to Famous Southern Oregon Rivers
</h3>
<p>
